<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background-color: #2c3e50; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
    .content { padding: 20px; background-color: #f9f9f9; }
    .footer { text-align: center; padding: 20px; color: #777; font-size: 12px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Your Tax Document is Ready</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello {{ userName }},</p>
      <p>Your tax document for <strong>{{ taxYear }}</strong> has been generated and is now available for download.</p>
      <p>You can access your tax document by logging into your WorkNow account and navigating to the Tax Documents section.</p>
      <p>This document includes:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Total earnings for {{ taxYear }}</li>
        <li>Platform fees deducted</li>
        <li>Itemized transaction breakdown</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Please review the document and use it for your tax filing.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; 2024 WorkNow. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>This is an automated notification. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>

